{
  "stem": "4189.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you could get a job, if you could show that you had a job there, they would give you a permit to go to England.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So through friends and relatives, she managed to get such a permit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because she was working on this permit, they extended her stay in Berlin until she was able to get out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this way, she was able to go to England and work as a domestic in a household in London-- near London.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Croyden, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was outside London.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now, we were still in France, my mother was now in England, and the uncle was in New York.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the family was really cut up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the situation in Paris, though, got also very uncomfortable because the French police was not as lenient to us, the refugees, as the Belgium police was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they caught somebody, they would send them back to the German border and send them back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that, of course, meant to go to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this relative, this Emmanuel, he was very frightened because we could not speak French.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We could not go outside and play.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had a little garden in his house, and that's the only place where we could go out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He would not let this out in the street because he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, one day, he said, look, it would be better for you to go back to Belgium, because in Belgium you have a better chance to get help and the police will not bother you, they will not send you back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he helped us, he brought us back to the Belgian border and brought us back over the border the same way as he did previously.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
